Fourth Department,

June, 1945.

(June 27, 1945.) Newton H. Reid, Appellant, v. City of Fulton, Respondent.

Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements. All concur. (The order grants defendant’s motion to dismiss plaintiff’s complaint in an action to compel specific performance.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Dowling, McCurn, Larkin and Love, JJ. [181 Misc. 711.]
